# Crawler output. Re-creatable by running:
#   python3 scripts/govuk_crawl.py --resume
# Extracted triples (extractors/) are always committed.
#
# By default, the raw HTML cache (pages/<slug>/page.html, ~50 KB each
# × ~1,700 = ~85 MB) is gitignored to keep the repo small. The smaller
# api.json files (typically 5-15 KB; the gov.uk Content API JSON) ARE
# committed so an LLM verifier can audit the extractor against the same
# structured data the script reads, with no re-fetch.

pages/*/page.html
pages/*/headers.json
crawl.log
state.json
